INSERT INTO `control` VALUES (1,'Main page','Main page','Marriage Brides - online dating site and searching romantic relationships','Marriage Brides, searching Online dating, unmarried girls and women, single sexy girls','Welcome to our international dating service marriage-brides.com, we have the most beautiful single Russian and Ukrainian women and girls who are looking for a serious relationship and want to marry, and to find love. The main goal of our site is to bring people together in the search for long-term relationships. Millions of people over the Internet can not find happiness. We are ready to help lonely people find love and happiness.With our members\' best interests in mind, we offer some of the most advanced technology available in online dating today, including chat, voice chat, live video, email services, and more . Our services are designed to provide a virtual dating environment, which is convenient. We have a site that has a unique control system against fraud. The site works only with people under the age of 18 years. We offer our services only to single women who are looking for long term relationships.','<p>Welcome to Marriage Brides, a Premium International Dating Site connecting beautiful Russian and Ukrainian women seeking serious relationships with men from all over the world.<br /> The main goal of our site is to bring people together in the search for long-term relationships. Millions of people over the Internet can not find happiness. We are ready to help lonely people find love and happiness.With our members\' best interests in mind, we offer some of the most advanced technology available in online dating today, including chat, voice chat, live video, email services, and more . Our services are designed to provide a virtual dating environment, which is convenient. We have a site that has a unique control system against fraud. The site works only with people under the age of 18 years. We offer our services only to single women who are looking for long term relationships.</p>','index',1,NULL),(2,'Contacts','Contacts','Contact details our company','Contacts','Contact details. Here you can sending us a massage','<p>&nbsp;Our highly professional staff is always ready to help you and answer all your questions email. <br />We are glad to get your suggestions for service improvement; also we appreciate any comments and testimonials. <br />&nbsp;Attention. This form does not allow you to write a letter to girls site. This letter forms, only receives, site administration</p>\r\n<p>All your questions and suggestions, you can write to our official email official.marriage.brides@gmail.com</p>','contacts',1,''),(3,'Just married','Just married','Just married','Just married','Just married','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I want to tell you the story of our love. I was a member on many websites but without success. I met Frank in two weeks after my registration on this site. Maybe it was fate but I liked him right away. We started talking though chat and writing letters. It was great but we needed more. We wanted to talk all the time. Then we started to talk on the phone and through mail. He said he wanted to come meet me. I waited for him for more than 2 months. I was so glad because I knew that I already love this man. When we met each other at the airport, we finally understood that we were born for each other. We spent a wonderful week together. We did everything together. We could be talking for 3 hours but it felt like 10 min. We are so happy we found our true love, each other.</p>\r\n<p>Olga and Frank</p>\r\n<p>Dearest Marriage-Brides team, with all sincerity and soulfulness of my heart I want to say that you really make dreams come true. To all people who are searching, I want to say that never give up and always believe in your dreams, believe in Your true love and it will find you, as it happened with me and Braulio. We have found each other by destiny and we have been writing to each other for many years. This summer was magnificent time for us, we were traveling and enjoying time together. We continue to write to each other and call each other every day, to make the distance short . I want to say that I am the happiest woman, because I met my true love. And I wish everyone to find happiness and true love.</p>\r\n<p>Elena and Braulio</p>\r\n<p>My first trip to Ukraine was a wonderful experience. The country was lovely and the people were friendly. What really made the trip unforgettable though was meeting Nadezhda! She was the reason I made the trip and finally meeting her made everything worthwhile. Nadya is just how I imagined she would be from our correspondence. She is physically beautiful but also warm and fun. She possesses a lot of energy too! Soon we will meet again and I have invited Nadezhda to visit me in the U.S. I hope she will want to stay! Thanks Marriage-Brides! You changed my life for the better by helping me meet a beautiful, smart woman who I want to spend the rest of my life with.</p>\r\n<p>Nadya and Paul</p>\r\n<p>When I registered, I thought that relationships can\\\'t be developed on the web site. Thanks&nbsp; to Marriage-Brides , I changed my mind. I met a very nice man here - Scott. We communicated for a long time and those were happy hours) He wants make his woman happy every day, he has a great sense of humor, he wants to travel. We have a lot in common and maybe that is why we decided to have a meeting in real life.Our meeting was so nice, we were smiling, talking and sometimes - just only looking in each other\\\'s eyes. I could see his soul in his eyes and his desire to be with me and that makes me feel very good. I want to thank Marriage-Brides for this opportunity!</p>\r\n<p>Irina and Scoot</p>\r\n<p>I want to thank Marriage-Brides for acquainting me with Anna. After meeting online and chatting for a month we decided to meet in person. I made the trip to Ukraine and it was wonderful. Meeting in person was a very special moment for us both and she exceeded all my expectations! Julia from the agency was a big help and a lot of fun. Our time spent together was casual and fun. We enjoyed getting to know more about one another in person. It\'s amazing to think what Marriage-Brides makes possible. Bringing together two people from great distances who share the same dreams, perhaps to fall in love and be happy together for many years to come. Thanks again Marriage-Brides, for allowing me the opportunity to meet Anna!</p>\r\n<p>Anna and Matt</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I went to Ukraine meeting Tatiana. With whom I\'ve been talking on the site for a while. She was more beautiful in real than I could imagine. We found we had many things in common. We both feel like we are the soul mates. We went to many interesting places. I would like to thank Marriage-Brides and the staff for their help. Now we plan for Tatiana visiting me in Sweden. I just would like to say it is possible to find your soul mate, here on this site. Tatiana\'s and mine journey to the future has just begun.</p>\r\n<p>Tatiana and ChristerI</p>\r\n<p>If you want to meet real Ukrainian women who want to get married, Marriage-Brides is the place to find them! Other services are much more expensive, and the selection of amazing women is not as good as Marriage-Brides. I love the Ukrainian women because they are beautiful, healthy, educated, hard working, focused on what is most important in life, and are committed to being good wives and mothers. Through Marriage-Brides I&rsquo;ve met the girl who I want to be with forever! I met Natalia&nbsp; and from the moment we met I knew she was someone I was interested in marrying because she ran into my arms and gave me a big hug and a kiss on the cheek, what a great way to start a relationship!On our first date we went to a restaurant and stayed there for five hours, talking and laughing, it was so much fun! Natalia&rsquo;s English is good, but we had an Interpreter named Helen with us who helped us to truly understand one another. There was a lot of energy between Natalia and me, so I really appreciated having and expert like Helen there with us so we could fully express ourselves to each other. Both Natalia and I feel we will be together forever, and we cannot wait to see each other again. I would recommend Marriage-Bridesto anyone who wants to find a wonderful Ukrainian woman to marry.</p>\r\n<p>Natalia and Tom</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I had a wonderful time with Tatiana. When Tatiana came to my door and I saw her for the first time, she was more beautiful than her photos. I was so nervous, but we instantly made a connection, it felt as if we new each other for years. I enjoyed every minute with Tatiana, she made me feel so relaxed.Tatiana and myself stay in contact and I am coming back to Ukraine &nbsp;&nbsp;to be with Tatiana again. I enjoyed Ukraine very much it is a very interesting country with amazing people, the Ukrainian people are always willing to help due to the language &nbsp;barrier and I managed very well with the help of the people. The Marriage-Brides team and translators where very helpful. They were very professional. I would like to say to all the gents, treat the woman like a lady and always consider the lady\'s feelings. Marriage-Brides is fantastic.</p>\r\n<p>Tatiana and Mickey</p>\r\n<p>Hello! Before all I would like to thank you for your professional help to meet Christina. She is a wonderful girl and also good at Italian language. Our meeting was not very long and I would like to develop my friendship with her. I am an eyes surgeon, busy in research and in writing in scientific magazines, but I believe that it\'s better to meet some girls to choose the best. I receive about 80 letters every day and I wish I was able to understand their character. Obviously I\'ll be happy to tell you that I will be satisfied. In Italy we say that the good day can be seen from the morning and I am really interested in Christina.</p>\r\n<p>Christina and Enrico</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I want to share with you a nice story of my meeting with Karl. We communicated for a long time and we felt that we both are very interested in each other and we want to meet and check our chemistry in real life. Karl came to see me in Kharkov. We spent an amazing weekend together, which was one of the best weekends in my life. Karl is a very interesting and an active man, who is attentive and caring as well. I know for sure that he knows how to treat his lady and how to make her happy. We talked a lot, walked and I showed him my city. We tried Ukrainian cuisine and I shared with him my favorite dishes and showed my favorite places in Kharkov. It was the romantic and wonderful meeting. I have high hopes that we will go on in our communication and all our dreams will come true in the near future. I want to thank Marriage-Brides for giving me such a chance to meet this good and interesting man and to get to know him even better in real life!</p>\r\n<p>Natalia and Karl</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','just-married',1,NULL),(4,'FAQ','FAQ','FAQ','FAQ','FAQ','<p>&nbsp;Our site was made for men who wish to explore all of their options of choosing a beloved or a close friend. By viewing each woman\'s photos, and reading their profiles, you can decide with whom you would like to correspond, to have phone conversations and to communicate live (using our service Live Chat). Also, you can make gifts to your special lady (using our Gifts and flowers service).<br />&nbsp;There are a variety of reasons why the women choose to join our site. Our experience says that the primary objective of these women is to find a loyal, dependable, stable man with whom they can build a happy and loving family. Now these women are searching outside of their country because for whatever reason they have not been able to find the special one yet. Creating a family is very important to the vast majority of these women, thus they are forced to expand their search for the beloved one. The Internet has also opened up a whole new world of opportunities to these women, they are no longer confined to their own cities and towns in the search. So they are really hoping that one day the right person will look upon their profiles and the wonderful love story will begin.<br />&nbsp;Our site attempts to be as diverse as possible. We have women on our database from all walks of life, different cultures, and varying age groups. We helps Western men liaison with the best in Eastern European women through a network of dating agency partners located in cities across Ukraine &amp; CIS. Our site brings romantic couples together in a number of ways (correspondence, live chat, phone translation).</p>','faq',1,NULL),(5,'News','News','News','News','News','','news',1,NULL),(6,'Search','','Search for your lady on website','Search lady','Here you can searchin your lady on \"Marriage Brides\"','','search',1,NULL),(7,'License agreement','Licence agreement','Licence agreement','Licence agreement','Licence agreement','<p>Please read the license agreement<br />If you wish to become a Member, communicate with other Members and fully use our company services (the \"Featured services\"), please read these Terms and Conditions and confirm your acceptance of them by clicking on the &ldquo;Sign In&rdquo; button below the registration form.</p>\r\n<p>Once you agree to be bound by all provisions of this Terms and Conditions, and click on the \"Sign In\" button, you will be bound by these Terms of Use (this \"Agreement\"), whether or not you register as a member (\"Member\").</p>\r\n<p>This Agreement sets out the legally binding terms of your use of the Web site and your membership in the Service and may be modified by our company from time to time. Such modifications are to be effective upon posted by our company on the Web site.</p>\r\n<p><br />By agreeing to the rules of the site, you authorize to send you promotional message on our website for your mail, in the future, you can opt out of mailings of our website.</p>\r\n<p>This Agreement includes Our Company Acceptable Use Policy for Content Posted on the Web site, Our Company Privacy Policy, and any notices regarding the Web site.</p>\r\n<p>You must be eighteen or over to register at our site. Membership in the Service is void where prohibited. By using the Web site, you represent and warrant that you have the right, authority, and capacity to enter into this Agreement and to abide by all of the terms and conditions of this Agreement.</p>\r\n<p>This Agreement will remain in full force and effect while you use the Web site and/or are a Member. You may terminate your membership at any time, at any reason, upon receipt of your written notice of termination by Our Company Customer support staff. Our company may terminate your membership at any specified reason, effective upon sending a notice to your email address provided for the registration, or to any other email address provided by you to Our Company staff. If your membership at Our Company was terminated by reason of violation of Our Company Terms of Agreement, or at your request, you will not be entitled to receive any refund on unused coins or paid fees for using our site additional services. Despite the fact of your membership being terminated, this Agreement will remain in full effect.<br />The Web site is for the personal use of individual Members only and may not be used in connection with any commercial endeavors. Organizations, companies, and/or businesses may not become Members and are not entitled to use the Service or the Web site for any purpose. Illegal and/or unauthorized use of the Web site, including collecting usernames and/or email addresses of members by electronic or other means for the purpose of sending unsolicited email and unauthorized framing of or linking to the Web site will be investigated, and appropriate legal action will be taken, including without limitation, civil, criminal, and injunctive redress.</p>\r\n